*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT ZRSA01_13.

DATA: gv_a VALUE 'A',
      gv_b VALUE 'B',
      gv_c VALUE 'C',
      gv_d VALUE 'D'.

WRITE:/ 'Input Value: ', gv_a, gv_b, gv_c, gv_d.

PERFORM test USING gv_a gv_b
             CHANGING gv_c gv_d.

WRITE:/ 'PERFORM END: ', gv_a, gv_b, gv_c, gv_d.

*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form test
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM test USING    VALUE(p_a)
                         p_b
          CHANGING VALUE(p_c)
                         p_d.

  p_a = 'W'.
  p_b = 'X'.
  p_c = 'Y'.
  p_d = 'Z'.

  WRITE:/ 'FORM In:     ', gv_a, gv_b, gv_c, gv_d.

ENDFORM.
